  "texts": [
    "For instance, consider the following sentence:",
    "\"The Dnak suppressor protein interacts with molecular chaperones to assist in protein folding and prevent misfolding or aggregation.\"",
    "The phrase \"Dnak suppressor protein\" is identified as a gene/protein entity by BERN2, helping to reduce the structural complexity of the sentence.",
    "However, we need to extract only the entity name \"Dnak\" to successfully group regulations extracted from different research papers.",
    "To extract just the entity name, we split the phrases and process the individual words for NER using BERN2 (Fig 4)."
  ],
